{"tid":1598255,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前壁屋懲教助理涉向囚犯母親索取燒鵝燒鴨 被廉署落案起訴","createTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:58:47.000Z","uid":33775,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb281757aa36a971468696383c1434c72693f5ad","tid":1598255,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"廉政公署今日（27日）落案起訴一名尹姓懲教署前一級懲教助理，控告他涉嫌於農曆新年向一名到訪的囚犯母親索取及收受燒鵝及燒鴨。<br />\n<br />\n55歲被告尹志亮被控兩項罪名，分別為一項訂明人員索取利益罪，及一項訂明人員接受利益罪。被告已獲廉署准予保釋，將於下星期三（2日）在觀塘裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n被告案發時為壁屋懲教所（壁屋）探訪組主管，負責監察及接待探訪壁屋囚犯的訪客。其中一項控罪指被告涉嫌於2018年2月15日，未得行政長官一般或特別許可而向一名壁屋囚犯的母親索取一隻燒鵝髀。而另一項控罪指被告涉嫌於2018年2月17日從該名母親接受一隻燒鴨。廉署接獲懲教署轉介的貪污投訴後展開調查。"},{"pid":"3297aa594519b64917d88882cad5e5e243e85b2e","tid":1598255,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=670aad05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=5e798d60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcHaJTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcHaJTs.jpg&h=032e94ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWfr1E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWfr1E9.jpg&h=defd0334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdP4Oj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn